---
import Layout from '../../../components/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Planetary Movements - Astrology Calendar"
  description="Current planetary positions, retrogrades and astrological influences. Detailed planetary calendar and analysis."
>  <main class="min-h-screen">

    <!-- Navigation Breadcrumb -->
    <div class="bg-gray-50 shadow-sm border-b py-3">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <nav class="flex items-center space-x-2 text-sm">
          <a href="/en" class="flex items-center text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 transition-colors">
            <span class="mr-1">🏠</span>Home
          </a>
          <span class="text-gray-400">›</span>
          <a href="/en/categories" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 transition-colors">
            📁 All Categories
          </a>
          <span class="text-gray-400">›</span>
          <a href="/en/astrology" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 transition-colors">
            🔮 Astrology
          </a>
          <span class="text-gray-400">›</span>
          <span class="text-gray-600 font-medium">🪐 Planetary Movements</span>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </div>    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 via-purple-500 to-indigo-500 text-white py-16">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
        <div class="text-8xl mb-4">🪐</div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">
          Planetary Movements
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl mb-2">Current Astrological Positions</p>
        <p class="text-lg opacity-90">Retrograde Periods and Effects</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
      <!-- Current Planetary Positions -->
      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8">Current Planetary Positions</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-3xl mr-3">☀️</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-xl">Sun</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">in Gemini</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
              Sun in Gemini enhances communication and learning activities.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-3xl mr-3">🌙</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-xl">Moon</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Variable Position</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
              Moon's daily movements affect our emotional state and intuition.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-3xl mr-3">☿️</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-xl">Mercury</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">in Gemini</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
              Mercury in its home sign brings clarity in communication and technology.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-3xl mr-3">♀️</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-xl">Venus</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">in Cancer</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
              Venus in Cancer brings positive developments in family and home matters.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-3xl mr-3">♂️</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-xl">Mars</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">in Leo</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
              Mars in Leo boosts creativity and leadership energy.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-3xl mr-3">♃</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-xl">Jupiter</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">in Gemini</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
              Jupiter in Gemini brings expansion in education and travel.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Retrograde Periods -->
      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8">Retrograde Periods</h2>
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-red-50 to-orange-50 rounded-xl p-8">
          <div class="text-center mb-6">
            <span class="text-4xl">⚠️</span>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-red-800 mt-2">Important Periods to Watch</h3>
          </div>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6">
              <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Mercury Retrograde</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2">June 23 - July 15, 2025</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
                Expect communication issues, technology glitches, and travel delays.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6">
              <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Venus Retrograde</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2">August 12 - October 3, 2025</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
                A time to review relationships. Past lovers may return.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Monthly Forecast -->
      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8">Monthly Planetary Calendar</h2>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-blue-500 text-white p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">June 2025 Highlights</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                <div class="bg-blue-100 rounded-full p-2">
                  <span class="text-xl">🌕</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold">June 21 - Summer Solstice</h4>
                  <p class="text-gray-600">Sun enters Cancer. Perfect time for new beginnings.</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                <div class="bg-red-100 rounded-full p-2">
                  <span class="text-xl">☿️</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold">June 23 - Mercury Retrograde Begins</h4>
                  <p class="text-gray-600">A period requiring caution in communication and technology.</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                <div class="bg-green-100 rounded-full p-2">
                  <span class="text-xl">♀️</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold">June 28 - Venus in Leo</h4>
                  <p class="text-gray-600">Positive developments in creativity and romance.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Tips and Advice -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8">How to Work with Planetary Movements</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-green-400 to-blue-500 text-white rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-3xl mb-4">🎯</div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Timing</h3>
            <p>Time important decisions according to planetary positions.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-400 to-pink-500 text-white rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-3xl mb-4">🧘‍♀️</div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Awareness</h3>
            <p>Be patient during retrograde periods and focus on review.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-400 to-red-500 text-white rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-3xl mb-4">🌟</div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Growth</h3>
            <p>Use planetary energies for personal development.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
